content.description: Scramble on to the ledge and shimmy into the wide squeeze and climb this to the top. Place a good cam and cut left on the horizontal. Might be dirty in this crack as I established this route 4 years ago or longer... Make a move to gain the next squeeze chimney. You could go to the anchors out left for Critical Access to belay your second.
content.protection: Walk north down the east wall reference picture
content.location: Wide gear is a must to protect the chimney. I’d say a #6 maybe a #5... you could prob get some pretty big stuff in there. I didn’t have wide gear when I did this and wished I did. I was able to place a beak in a seem but wide cams will be better

content.description: Climb up the face to the left leaning ramp feature. Climb up ramp and then head up through the steep rock above.
